social_posts.post_text: happy birthday to my favorite 🌱
mushroom hunting with my sweet girl 🌱

twin ‘nem 🌱

i’m holding on to this moment. noa has looked like her daddy for the past year!

the mushroom puff pastries were definitely a favorite. i made a paste using mushrooms, cheese, fresh herbs and butter to spread on top of the pastry and topped them with sautéed mushrooms. the mushroom galette was also a banger. we have tons of mushrooms that we sautéed and froze…please send me your fav recipes! 🌱

#mushrooms #mushroom #foraging #oystermushrooms
a quick date with the sun 🌱

january 2023. 
my new year is officially starting today! last month was a whirlwind. excited for even more of this though—more traveling, more creative productions, more hanging with loved ones, more art, more earthing.
celebrating being a black artist 🌱
draped in black women designers 🌱
feeling very grateful for family & great friends 🌱
twinning with my sweet girl 🌱

taking ceramics for the past 5 months has been so fulfilling. it gets me out of the house for a few hours and i get to practice a new craft that i’m slowly falling in love with. 🌱

when’s the last time you tried something new?

today was perfect. started it off with our friends doing a cold plunge into the river. the water was so cold that it stung—but after 10 minutes, the water started to feel warm. afterwards, matthew & i went on a little date in the driveway, coloring easter eggs for Noa during her nap.  then we had the cutest time helping her find all of the eggs in the grass.  thank you, God. 🌱

starting a petition for a 4 day work week so that i can engage in more of this. 
farmers market visits. gardening with my family & friends. foraging morels from our yard 😲. giving my plant babies a bath and new fits. and of course, spending quality time with my man, archey & my favorite girl. a perfect weekend. 🌱

me & my man 🌱

📷: @justenwilliams 
#aislebelovingtaylor
me & my favorite girl 🌱
nothing in this world compares to being mama to my sweet noa greyson. i’m madly in love with this one. thank you, God. 🌱
oh, the places you’ll go, my sweet girl. 🌱
never lose your sense of wonder, sweet girl. 🌱

listening to @forbetterorbestpod and Shireen is speaking to me & my post partum weight that keeps fluctuating (almost 2 years later). —it’s really just bad habit weight that’s fluctuating🙃 but currently trying to convince myself to get on some sort of consistent fitness journey, and whew. i’m tired!
we love you more than anything, dada🌱🫶🏽

one of my favorite moments of everyday is doing affirmations with Noa. we usually do them in the mirror but i decided to record her last night. the way that she blushes each & every time 😩 please. it’s entirely too much.
it’s chanterelle season 🌱😋

a flop. some days i follow directions and most days i just want to feel shit out. this pottery wheel is seriously humbling me 😂😒

#cermamics #pottery

1. my new, custom babies finally came in the mail. 16 year old me is very pleased.
2. a refreshing clementine in front of my most recent painting.
3. avocado toast on fresh bread from my beautiful neighbor sitting on a plate that i made. 
4. soft ice that you can crush with 
the roof of your mouth and your tongue-iykyk

1. i’ve listened to this song about thirty times in the past few days.
2. what i’m hearing in my DMs is that i need to make more home goods and send y’all a purchase link?
